  3,149,"ya 'ayuha aladhin sddaqu allah warasulah waeamiluu bshreh, 'iin tutieuu aladhin jahaduu alwhyty, walam yuminuu birusuli min alyhwd walnsara walmunafiqin walmushrikin fima yamrwnkm bih wynhwnkm enh, ydlwkm ean tariq alhq, wtrtddu ean dynkm, ftewdu balkhsran almubin walhlak almhqq"
